{
  "id": "RAW_9d5618e4",
  "title": "好多大厂 APP 文本链接不用主题色，其实是没招了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjgzNDgzOQ==&mid=2247533008&idx=1&sn=661e639c6bc46501b12b22406ca5a70a",
  "date": "2026-03-16 00:20:00",
  "author": "体验进阶",
  "siteName": "体验进阶",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22995b5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FSFs7B2IF81q2sPFfN2ljThOsdiakibib1K1TWkW4uicA71J5kQ3PSz4AaoLkgL0bZVBhdBe39gPsxhkcVFJlkJ7w1nMhTiabYUup1rMciahVQ0keI%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>能用的话早用了…</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">经常看到一些主题色比较浅的产品设计，白底页面上文字链接用主题色，导致文本链接还不如普通文本显眼，看得很累。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100049262\" data-ratio=\"0.475\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea504d4f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81pu9icXx3z41MiaibibTy033JnJ3TA3uLQeNMKic1IJCw9dbIn37sVH3cl8uKc7eEib9OcMiaGp16fTddD8QVeSKRQKBnoAGcCvDs1r64%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">QQ音乐</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.475\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049264\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=64a699fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81rfNd0icwL8m563cgOwpFjFssuUw5cgayjdy5G7rsFGsLbJiaWShNXSMAJpfxuVZq44MAmPaD24ic57EJOjbtibVU6tvqGsC54t5xU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">活动行</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">有些聪明一点的，会给普通文字用浅灰色，这样文本链接可以体现出来。但是由于文字的颜色整体偏浅，导致可读性还是较差。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.18796296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049265\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=04aa50e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81pGibqYcBEfIeCCzZfNvIia7v2gxTSibwZsSzdlTsp8vNI3T52H1fT1osfCrGNHGV5CFehflUicCE28CNaGLcX7KlSiamg4ZExmiaAuI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">朴朴</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">文字链接的颜色要怎样才合理？如果主题色不适合做文本链接，又该怎么办？</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">接下来，我会先给大家介绍一个验证文字色彩对比度的方法，然后再来看看大厂有哪些处理方式。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">怎样的颜色才方便阅读？</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">Web Content Accessibility Guideline（网页内容无障碍指南，简称WCAG）是由万维网联盟（W3C）下属的无障碍网页倡议组织（WAI）发布的国际网页无障碍标准，旨在通过规范网页内容的设计与开发，确保所有用户（包括残障人士、老年人、色盲用户等）都能平等访问网页信息。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5027777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049289\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69a65280&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81onWh3kBxanXy4F5ibKrNiaCqh6s2iaY131oLxUiaBkkT5SASCqUYYEMib2ZJI4Dibg60agkjfWeQhNuzBGCu9icyJEqtibUYa5NVAQiaA8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">WCAG对色彩对比的要求基于文本类型（普通文本/大文本）和 conformance level（&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">合规等级</span><span leaf=\"\">），分为AA级（最低推荐标准）和AAA级（增强标准）两个层级。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">底线：普通文本≥4.5:1（AA级），大文本≥3:1（AA级）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">——这是全球公认的“最低可读”门槛；</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">理想：普通文本≥7:1（AAA级），大文本≥4.5:1（AAA级）——兼顾舒适性与包容性；</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">WCAG采用相对亮度公式计算文本与背景的对比度，具体步骤如下：</span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">将文本颜色（前景色）和背景颜色的RGB值转换为sRGB空间（即归一化到0-1范围）；</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">对每个颜色通道（R/G/B），若其值≤0.03928，则除以12.92；否则按公式((value + 0.055) / 1.055) ^ 2.4计算；</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">计算相对亮度（L）：L = 0.2126*R + 0.7152*G + 0.0722*B（其中R/G/B为步骤2的结果）；</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">计算对比度比值：(L1 + 0.05) / (L2 + 0.05)（L1为较亮颜色的相对亮度，L2为较暗颜色的相对亮度）。</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了方便，可以直接使用一个计算工具，网址我放在底部「原文链接」了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7194444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049266\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca74fe86&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81qtBoeUKRYcpTmGpcTgYFUibcu4ZicXBvdGeB5lsGyIGczIoxj0qNHHDy3c66eebKpADAY5ASLibzLxarRsia4Fpx0d6CjI1qCOA6o%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">按照这个公式，以下文本色都是不合格的：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.19074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049268\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=82072dac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81rbib3spRIYx2T1qwe4tRpR0T4YhyapXDTE1t0mfQ2TVFmRWkwcwQ703ut8oXgp8LVIpwk01mNRRHeZ5fGtq0159RSYyr9QOvII%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">以下文本色作为大文本是符合的，但是作为普通文本不合格：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.19074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049269\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96ab5401&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81pth2scpPWCk7cvUpa2A6TsU8qS4LU4sauQkPia8DTrodq7VIRGYM7R2q7T72mHMWCA97xmFenYEyoFwXSiajKhLvhx9MxbePyLI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">我发现，即便是大厂设计，文字颜色的对比度达到理想等级的非常少。可能是为了平衡美观性吧，能够达到 3 : 1 就算不错了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">Google的A/B测试</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">谷歌搜索引擎在2019年其实尝试过另一个色彩的文字链接，但是很快下线了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049271\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ff35a46&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81pFao4lOkaAm8ulJ6D9GvBYz5bE66dhzntoibZSVJt0NsuL8omicLSWMxszbocxMwkfDBibktOk67f2BqTdbx0A9ViaDHasMbPC0L4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">上图来源：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\"><a href=\"https://goodui.org/leaks/google-has-been-a-b-testing-link-colors-again-and-this-light-blue-didnt-pass/\" target=\"_blank\">https://goodui.org/leaks/google-has-been-a-b-testing-link-colors-again-and-this-light-blue-didnt-pass/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">虽然没有谷歌官方的消息来源，但按照常理来分析，主题色文字链接被下线的原因可能是可读性的问题。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">尽管这个颜色以</span><span leaf=\"\">WCAG的标准来看，算是合格：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9175925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049272\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bc167715&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81osmWrkmIIN8JiaIN9Qa7xFnGGQHGbhChDPIXNEbcIzVREkG1KlbsholboBloZ5yJRdA6ss2y4gIzUWiawfMJovPFvgIRY9zgKia4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\">现在他们的文本链接颜色明显比主题色偏紫一些：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049273\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1b3438a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81p5w3l7mmenHYoS0LFt58gsDjvQmibOYaicPEGvnjM8uicpCKzjA7LT0icdiacKHCVv4gY1E1fU9c5mRT0k3PJcghS8TVVLohiaKJiaibo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">这个颜色的对比度就更高了，数值接近前者的2倍：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9055555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049274\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f178ffb7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81r0RJUBibhvLIYc6MoCzpTfpHP87AIJIrzz8B5c4s1xrnqoLaXtWOBfJ9vLZqCqK661jPzdaYZ6Pt8gXjCZlYPTxvfJMc6eH8Gw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">元宝选择把主题色加深</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">腾讯的AI元宝的主题色是挺亮的绿色，如果直接用在文字上，可读性是不够的：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049290\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36accdd1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81q7I1kwB54LvsufnRk3vkq2J7SIRicCbokaJxliblHSLicYVic8dKRhneONZscUylqgr2WIteGHE6XcL10iaAmUyhja9qSPjb1vjxhU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9064814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049278\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5468ca89&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81oj4EyOM846x5WxIbShp235k5bAj1bV0bZcHybkhAiab9od3J5wwKy4yVgAZeeNdJoAq1s8wuga3xXFEWDcSd9TYtKrwNaHlJvc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">于是，他们选了一个明显更深的绿色，把对比度一下子拉到了一个很客观的数值：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4c4dd51a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81pPuTOd914wSjkYOrQOcQBjUnnxoGZWiaiaVpRRZzcnOKVRMVtMUl7mMtB9pTl9Cxg7DU35AhZZ4QvjcSkUbrV9TsLOJrQ4xuicb8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8916666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049279\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f78846d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81oJckrkQjZoA0iaganBfDNicxxicjw6OA8hldahTFxme4azibIHRnN48kCIfic8YCwIQGdrB5kP94DyxJ9ABRoVwibyibcIvS6z8ib6x60%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">微信选择灰蓝色</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlrx5klh1cow\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlrx5kmfk9b\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">众所周知，微信的主题色是绿色，这个颜色的对比度也不足以用在文本上：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049292\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37e70d4b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81rRV3Rncl2slia4h2bKsibBUHC1ajibOYyCPb1waUWmYvW8BUFKaoM2e6HwWh1lXY7dSO72gegSB9nffhAoQbgMeYGCXghkXbG4dU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9324074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049281\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b06daa0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81oUOv1MVmibIRXAqFTWDp6mj112smm67OmSqVnJC9kK2e6XwOeca5MdsqjOFywlJMJVkk5QN1n273iclwxMS1f4zdJ6ibuYUxAicVU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">微信比较特别的做法是，选了一个偏灰的蓝色给文本链接用，看起来跟主题绿毫无关联。</span><span leaf=\"\">这个灰蓝色的对比度，确实是够格给文本用的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049293\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f81a271f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81qrYelMpulZ3cAhNSgL1IEj0FoZGenCDplrQO12EYicCT9E1Dzd4cQDTMC2a9Mpc4XQClb8zvhphm6AFZAeAdfoVBLmzRySCD18%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9166666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049282\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=752854e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81qU16ubRibVnrhe4Zk5KdH0OoB4mxPkiaLWSwSrTwxA0RHIfzYpMibNt0LOGX2OIUicokohQqlgr245Z65GSfOVLyicQwrWZ2cHkjLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">为什么要用偏灰的蓝色呢？可以看看下图的对比：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7185185185185186\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049283\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9362e08a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81pHJsmXwMLUWs9HzzSppcaGLCI3sjicnvibbZAjt3pJoINBnC6VNwpJWYE1LrCvxJGD2ZuD79ck99jXcktaqD0O75lGwlj4t73XY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">如果用亮蓝色的话，会比按钮的主题绿还抢眼。只有用灰蓝色，才能确保当主题绿出现时，依旧能够很好地引导用户视线。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">头条选择亮蓝色</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">今日头条的主题色是红色，但它的文本链接有些是红色，有些又是亮蓝色。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049284\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5657581b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81rlm8IiaKNicDUKxGX32vxv5uGOEIPARia2ia9aGZ3s5A1eqJiabU7RDueXt2HORkDckCeCCBsMKNxAnkuibk6qAxmXc57h6kNnjZmds%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">总结一下规律，用蓝色的文本链接，主要是不想引起注意的地方。所以，我才头条设计师是觉得有些文本链接用红色太过抢眼，所以才用亮蓝色的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">那为什么不像微信那样用灰蓝色呢？看看下图对比就知道了：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049285\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e14d722f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSFs7B2IF81psoU1h3rfTkfUt0BpSm3DyDBZUkIhwFdy74EEf7lkYs0wtJuIsoVrwia7zoOeFWYsxwOGgXcK8EZto1WSOicEmBl1giaiastIDG2U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">因为页面上的主题红已经很显眼了，文本链接就算用亮蓝色，也不会喧宾夺主。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">反倒是如果改用灰蓝色，会让文本链接太不起眼，看起来还有点像是无效链接。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;\">总结一下</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">当主题色相对于背景色的对比度较低时，可能就不适合给文本用了，具体可以用在线工具来测试。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">主题色为红色、橙色，有警示含义时，也可能不适合作为文本链接。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">如果主题色不适合给文本用，那么千万不要勉强用，也没必要为此改主题色。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">可以学习大厂的处理方法，例如：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlrxa5h219dj\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlrxa5i2wiu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">主题色调整色相（Google）、主题色加深（元宝）、灰蓝色（微信）和亮蓝色（今日头条）。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlrxa5h219dj\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlrxa5i2wiu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">你在做设计时有没有遇到过类似的问题？是怎样处理的？欢迎留言分享～</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章围绕「文本链接是否应使用主题色」给出可操作判断框架，核心结论是优先保证对比度与信息层级，再决定是否沿用品牌主色。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章围绕「文本链接是否应使用主题色」给出可操作判断框架，核心结论是优先保证对比度与信息层级，再决定是否沿用品牌主色。",
  "summary": "作者从多个常见 APP 的真实界面出发，讨论浅色主题在白底场景下用于文本链接时的可读性问题，并引入 WCAG 对比度标准作为判断基线。文章不仅解释了普通文本与大文本的最低门槛，还给出可直接复用的计算思路与在线工具入口，随后通过 Google、元宝、微信、今日头条等案例总结四类实践策略：调整色相、加深主题色、使用灰蓝替代、在高显著主题下使用亮蓝补位。整体内容兼具规范依据与设计取舍，实用性较强，适合产品设计和 UI 设计场景快速落地。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "文本链接是否用主题色，首先是可读性问题而不是品牌一致性问题。",
      "explanation": "当主题色与背景对比不足时，链接信息会弱于正文，影响识别效率和阅读体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "WCAG 对比度阈值可作为设计决策的客观底线。",
      "explanation": "普通文本至少 4.5:1、大文本至少 3:1（AA）可作为最低标准，避免纯主观审美决策。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大厂实践说明「不用主题色」常是层级控制与可读性平衡后的结果。",
      "explanation": "通过换色相、加深色值或选灰蓝等方式，既保持视觉体系又避免链接喧宾夺主或过度隐身。"
    },
    {
      "point": "链接颜色应结合页面主视觉重心进行相对设计。",
      "explanation": "当页面已有高显著主色元素时，链接可使用更亮对比色；否则需控制其抢眼程度以维持信息优先级。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "底线：普通文本≥4.5:1（AA 级），大文本≥3:1（AA 级）------这是全球公认的\"最低可读\"门槛；",
    "当主题色相对于背景色的对比度较低时，可能就不适合给文本用了，具体可以用在线工具来测试。",
    "如果主题色不适合给文本用，那么千万不要勉强用，也没必要为此改主题色。"
  ],
